xorg-server (2:1.13.3-0ubuntu1) raring; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * Drop patches applied upstream.
    - 237_dix_save_touchpoint_last_coords_before_transform.patch
    - randr-cleanup-provider-properly.patch
