  * Bump xserver-xorg-dev dependency on x11proto-core-dev and
    x11proto-dri2-dev, add dependency on x11proto-xinerama-dev.
  * Bump serverminver, videoabiver, inputabiver.

  [ Christopher James Halse Rogers ]
